about.summary: Provides tools for multiple imputation of missing data in multilevel modeling. Includes a user-friendly interface to the packages 'pan' and 'jomo', and several functions for visualization, data management and the analysis  of multiply imputed data sets.

Provides tools for multiple imputation of missing data in multilevel modeling. Includes a user-friendly interface to the packages 'pan' and 'jomo', and several functions for visualization, data management and the analysis  of multiply imputed data sets.

name: r-mitml
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4-1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-mitml
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/mitml_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/mitml/mitml_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ec10c29bc58a9ca6bda666db6d24bf54910b89fe72d901b9da7edc6ea81389af

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-haven
    - r-jomo
    - r-pan
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-haven
    - r-jomo
    - r-pan

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('mitml')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('mitml')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=mitml
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Provides tools for multiple imputation of missing data in multilevel modeling. Includes a user-friendly interface to the packages 'pan' and 'jomo', and several functions for visualization, data management and the analysis  of multiply imputed data sets.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
